Rating: 2
Yummy enough fresh from the oven, but leftovers don't hold up or reheat well (if you reheat, use oven only; microwaving makes it gummy & worse than airline food). Found myself wondering whether grated lemon peel should be packed or left fluffy when measuring (how come recipes never specify?) I tamped, and everybody thought it was way too much lemon. Very unsubtle.

Rating: 4
coupled with vanilla ice cream, this crisp rivals the crisps from my childhood. the almond adds a nice roundness, not overpowering. there is a lot of topping, which may account for one reviewer's "flouriness", so i would suggest using as many apples as fits into your dish. definately will be making this again.

